Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 新聯合國要求通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聯合國的潛水艇怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在仍緊跟在Alvis後方約50公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼處理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來總算得到對話的機會了啊 API-1的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新聯合國秘書長赫絲特·蓋洛普
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Alvis代表 真壁史彥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在當前這個戰爭時期 我們迫切希望和你們並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 希望推行樂園計畫的貴方能滿足我們一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:42.09,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,1000)}Arcadian Project
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也有要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中止新聯合國對本島的一切干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你說得出這麼自私的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有那麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不協助聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我們會容忍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令 你真的能拒絕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 你同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅵ交給新聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 也不想想我們花了多少年才完成啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能接受對方的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聯合國的人類軍運輸艦隊後天會到達我們Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅵ移動到向島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊去做Mk.Ⅲ和Mk.Ⅳ的最終調整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聯合國到底為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事遠見醫生知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 對方背後可能有個棘手的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最起碼要把布倫希爾德系統的連接數據抽走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 再等一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎同學應該很快就會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎同學還不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上還有粉筆灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城同學很關心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 今天走那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模擬戰之前 先去做做上次的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 坐在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 臉色很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是輕微貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 這個不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 春日井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子她好像太拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間她肯定是很喜歡現在的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於羽佐間翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到她的身體狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓她暫時脫離計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考慮一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真壁司令的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是狩谷老師你的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是樂園計畫的方針
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生你也知道我們的時間不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我倒是明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的病是宿疾 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這個計畫裡犧牲了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還裝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都再三囑咐過你不能勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽還有機庫的工作 今晚你就在這兒休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也住下來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去西尾奶奶那裡買些好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 媽媽就去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢 就麻煩你照顧翔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢 有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然春日井說願意幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是翔子說希望一騎也來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我過後去病房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…那樣我也會更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 輪到一騎同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 要抽哪張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨蹭了 快抽吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-B)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好別和他們走得太近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和他們 已經不能再做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能像一騎同學那樣開法芙娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好起來了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體會有好起來的那天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是健康的媽媽的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神劍型…真想快些親眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,1000)}Nothung Model
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：典出「尼伯龍根的指環」中齊格飛所持的諾通寶劍 nothung的德語原意為「生於危難中」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它十分值得一看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門發出預言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘書長 祝福者出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門發出應答 類別為Ambivalent 斷定為質問者型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.65,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,1000)}矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你輔助通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說「明白」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜下心來做就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「靜下心來」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護衛艦被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都來到這裡了 怎麼能空手而歸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 新聯合國發來訊息要求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被擊沉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也不能坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓Mk.Ⅺ出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體還沒好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助一騎同學是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼我能幫你的？羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 啟動進程就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員請進入駕駛座
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將到達法芙娜機庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要出擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回到這個島上來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時 我會在這裡當助理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你一定要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會保護你回來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
